{"h8222a71fge24ag4fc8g8253gba9d0d821658": ["Stay away from me!", "535f23bc-2d27-4c40-a1f3-1cf58bfd1698", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "61d2a6f8-6f79-fc57-233d-19cd9d3310d4"], "h55cb75beg2125g413fg89b1g147af8f87057": ["Don't touch me. Don't touch me!", "535f23bc-2d27-4c40-a1f3-1cf58bfd1698", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "3267f8d2-ed25-8e9b-afa1-91ed401c45d9"], "h95b7a673g09f8g466ag85efg35cd88e97c8b": ["I need to remove that mask.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "8b988258-9c61-4c27-4705-5cd6657df760"], "h3f92e535g5ac9g4637g8dadg87b9f0364e05": ["There is no mask - leave me alone!", "535f23bc-2d27-4c40-a1f3-1cf58bfd1698", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "84124bfe-1b42-cb09-a109-4c547d970439"], "h3ce38c30g5436g476fga4a6gfb779ab76859": ["Don't panic - I'm here to help. The hag's dead.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "7aaf1151-1f0e-1d02-575c-a64d2466e8e1"], "h9ae7a54bg9e89g4cc1g89dbg275381bb61f9": ["Auntie's dead? No no no no no.", "535f23bc-2d27-4c40-a1f3-1cf58bfd1698", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "24040c3b-a560-023d-0ece-968c9f2aa8b4"], "h250b7f31gd6fag4f1fga743gb024a69ecf79": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "3c9d5ab3-664e-d2f0-60e8-46966afe99ac"], "h79b8cfdfg67bdg4725g95ddg5a8cc1ed2cf4": ["Why is Auntie so quiet? I'm scared.", "535f23bc-2d27-4c40-a1f3-1cf58bfd1698", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "04749550-1eca-bda2-61ab-a8cf630d6ec9"], "hcfbc2cc1g1163g413fgb295g0b16afb9f349": ["She's dead. And good riddance.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "d4dc68aa-3f57-270f-0900-0dc8d95f2856"], "he0b83198g2581g4ff0gbdfeg727df40b1d1d": ["Don't be afraid. I'm here to help - I need to remove the mask.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "84e185e4-e361-a57c-27ff-24ef99479bbf"], "h660be6d7ga661g452egae75gee10a8d75d0d": ["<i>Leave.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "8ad4ccbe-2164-6552-2704-f4b047e6d834"], "hb7ef696bged78g45f5ga7aag06627ddb7ce7": ["Don't be afraid of Auntie - she'll take good care of you.", "535f23bc-2d27-4c40-a1f3-1cf58bfd1698", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\HagLair\\HAG_Hag_MaskedVictim2.html", "14ecf873-6ce2-4b25-a70d-5f479d58d370"]}